<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="drive-n">drive <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /draɪv/    美 /draɪv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 驱赶；驾驶；驱车旅行：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Let’s <strong>go for a drive</strong> in the country. 
我们开车到郊野去兜兜风吧。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Nanjing is about <strong>4 hours’drive from</strong> Xuzhou.
从徐州到南京开车大约要4个小时。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>driving /'draɪvɪŋ/ n [U]   </p></div>